  "title": "노후의 큰 걱정거리. 치매",
  "addDate": "2012. 11. 1.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "parentCategoryNo": "32",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110150846017",
  "html_size": 219403,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110150846017\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110150846017\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"맑은 고딕\">치매</font></span></span></a></span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">인구가 급속히 늘고 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span>우리나라<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 65</span>세 이상 노인에서의 치매 유병율은<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 9.5 ~ 13% </span>로 상당히 높은 수준이다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. 65</span>세 이상 노인의 열 명 중 한 명은 치매 질환을 앓고 있는 셈<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">80</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">세 이상 노인들 중에는<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 30% </span>정도가 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">치매</span></span><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></span><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">환자</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">로 추정될 정도다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\">최근 미국 치매학회와 국립노화연구소가<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 30</span>년 만에 치매 진단기준을 개정했다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>그 기준에 따르면 부분적 기억상실이나 공간감각<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>판단력이 떨어지는 정도의 가벼운 초기 증상도 치매로 진단 되게 된다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>치매는 뇌세포가 손상되기 시작한 후<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 7</span>년 정도 지나야 증상이 나타나기 때문에 빨리 진단해 조기에 치료받을 수 있도록 하겠다는 취지다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>치매환자가 지속적으로 늘고 있어 좀 더 적극적인 치료와 관리가 필요해졌기 때문이겠다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></font></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e76a2910b8650e1a.png\" width=\"257\" height=\"196\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 257px; rheight: 196px\" id=\"20121101_249/isuhani_13517417690173O8rq_PNG/%C4%A1%B8%C51.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5808641')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/e76a2910b8650e1a.png\"></span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></font></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">치매의 원인을 세분하면<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 70</span>여 가지에 이른다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>그러나 다른 원인들은 빈도가 낮기 때문에 치매의 원인을 크게 두 가지로 나누어 말한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>하나는 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">알츠하이머병</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">으로 알려진 것으로 아직까지 효과적인 치료 방법이 없다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>초기에 발견해서 진행을 늦추는 수밖에 없다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>다른 하나는 혈관성 치매로 뇌의 작은 혈관들이 여러군데에서 막히면서 뇌 손상이 조금씩 여러군데에서 생겨나 치매가 발생하는 것이다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>혈관성 치매는 예방도 가능하고 초기에 발견하여 치료하면 더 이상의 진행을 막을 수 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>치매의 원인에 대한 역학조사 결과들을 보면 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">알츠하이머</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">형 치매가 많고 혈관성 치매가 그 뒤를 따른다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></font></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c091b3b55ebeb1e1.png\" width=\"288\" height=\"175\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 288px; rheight: 175px\" id=\"20121101_182/isuhani_13517417809480B8TM_PNG/%C4%A1%B8%C52.png\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5808641')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c091b3b55ebeb1e1.png\"></span></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></font></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\">기억력 저하나 판단력<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>사고력이 떨어진다고 느낄 때 치매가 아닌지 관심을 가져야 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>구체적으로 보면 다음과 같은 증상들이 나타난다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>시간 감각이 떨어지고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>최근 일이 잘 기억나지 않는다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>익숙한 곳인데도 길을 잃는다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>좀 전에 했던 대와 내용을 기억하지 못한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>물건 둔 곳을 기억하지 못해 찾는데 어려움을 겪고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>물건의 이름이 잘 생각나지 않아서 한참을 기억하려 애써야 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>밥 하기<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>청소 하기 등 평소에 쉽게 잘 하던 일을 어려워 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>자기가 있는 곳이 어디인지 헷갈려 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>숫자나 돈 계산이 잘 안되고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>판단력이 떨어진다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>평생 한결같던 성격이 갑작스레 변한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>이런 증상들이 나타나면 검사를 받아보도록 하자<span lang=\"EN-US\">. 60</span>세 이상이면 보건소에서 치매 선별검사를 무료로 받을 수도 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>특히 고혈압 당뇨병 고지혈증 심장병 흡연 비만 등은 혈관성 치매를 유발할 수 있어 주의가 필요하다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></font></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9ef9c1b20f84c944.jpg\" width=\"259\" height=\"194\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 259px; rheight: 194px\" id=\"20121101_8/isuhani_1351741791546sCu1P_JPEG/%C4%A1%B8%C54.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5808641')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/9ef9c1b20f84c944.jpg\"></span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></font></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\">한방에서는 치매<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></font></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">痴&#21574;</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"> 또는 </font></span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">癡&#21574;</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">에 대해 예로부터 의서에 상세히 서술돼 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>오장육부 중에 주로 심장<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>간장과 쓸개와 관련이 많다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>담<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">痰</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">이라는 체내 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">노폐물</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">과 스트레스에 따른 화<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 굴림; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">火</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">가 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">혈액순환</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">을 방해하고 심장<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>간장<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>쓸개를 손상시키면 정신에 문제가 생기면서 감정의 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">조화</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">와 균형까지 깨지게 된다고 설명한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. [</span>경악전서<span lang=\"EN-US\">]</span>라는 책에 <span lang=\"EN-US\">‘</span>치매는 본래 담<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">痰</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">이 없더라도 울화<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">鬱火</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">가 맺히거나 뜻을 이루지 못하거나 근심하거나 의심을 품거나 놀라고 두려워함으로써 점차 치매에 이른다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>말에 두서가 없고 거동이 정상이 아니며 땀이 많이 나고 걱정을 잘하는 등 그 증상이 천양 각색으로 온갖 기괴한 것이 다 발생한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.’</span>고 자세한 설명이 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>화냄<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>슬픔<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>분노<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>걱정<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>두려움 등 감정적 스트레스가 치매의 원인이라는 될 수 있다는 점을 기억해야겠다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>치료에 대한 내용도 나온다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. ‘</span>치료될 수 있는 경우가 있고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>치료될 수 없는 경우가 있는데 역시 위기<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">胃氣</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">와 원기<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">元氣</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">의 강하고 약함에 달려 있으니 회복되기를 기다려야지 서둘러서는 안된다<span lang=\"EN-US\">.’ </span>한의학적인 치료로도 치매의 치료가 쉽지는 않다는 설명이다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>내 몸의 기운이 강하면 치료가 될 수 있고<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>기운이 약하면 치료될 수 없다고 했으니 평소의 건강관리는 효과적인 치매의 치료를 위해서도 꼭 필요하다 하겠다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><font size=\"2\" face=\"맑은 고딕\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><font size=\"2\" face=\"맑은 고딕\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121101_68/isuhani_1351741810829oO3hz_JPEG/%C4%A1%B8%C53.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"304\" height=\"166\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 304px; rheight: 166px\" id=\"20121101_68/isuhani_1351741810829oO3hz_JPEG/%C4%A1%B8%C53.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5808641')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121101_68/isuhani_1351741810829oO3hz_JPEG/%C4%A1%B8%C53.jpg?type=w3\"></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><font size=\"2\" face=\"맑은 고딕\"></font></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">치매는 건망증이나 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">우울증</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">과는 다르다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>방금 전의 일을 잊어버리는 것은 누구에게나 다소간 있는 것으로 병은 아니다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>어떤 사실을 잊었더라도 누가 힌트를 주면 금방 기억해내는 것은 건망증으로<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>병으로 보지 않는다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>치매는 힌트를 줘도 기억해내지 못하는 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">기억장애</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>우울증도 정도가 심해지면 의욕이 없고 기억장애가 나타나고 판단력과 사고력이 저하돼 치매와 같아 보인다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>하지만 우울증을 치료하면 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">치매증상</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">이 호전되니 치매와 구별된다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></font></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">그렇다면 치매 예방은 어떻게 할까<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>우선 혈압과 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">당뇨관리</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">를 위한 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">식이요법</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">이 중요하다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>그리고 과음을 삼가고 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">금연</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">과 </span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://economy.hankooki.com/lpage/entv/201105/e2011052617364294230.htm\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\"><span style=\"COLOR: windowtext; TEXT-DECORATION: none; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; text-underline: none\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">체중조절</span></span></a></span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">도 필요하다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>책을 읽거나 바둑 장기 등 일상생활에서 두뇌를 자주 사용하는 것도 좋다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>여기에 적절한 운동을 더해야 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>빨리 걷기를 꾸준히 하면 고혈압<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>고혈당<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>고지혈증 을 모두 낮추니 일석이조다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>크게 힘들이지 않고서 할 수 있는 게이트볼과 같은 운동도 좋다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>게이트 볼은 격렬한 동작은 없으면서도 근육과 관절을 골고루 사용해 전신운동의 효과가 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>또 경기를 하는 동안 자연스럽게 만보 이상 걸을 수 있어 유산소운동의 효과도 크다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>팀워크가 필요하니 서로간의 협력과 적당한 경쟁<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>두뇌회전 등을 통해 치매를 예방하는 효과가 있겠다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></span></font></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><font size=\"2\">무엇보다 가정이 화목하고 가족 간 대화를 많이 하는 게 좋다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>보건복지부와 분당서울대병원이 함께 한 조사에서 혼자 사는 노인이 배우자 또는 가족과 함께하는 노인에 비해 치매에 걸릴 확률이<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 2.4</span>배나 높은 것으로 조사되었다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>혼자 살면 다른 사람과 말을 하거나 교류할 기회가 적어져 정서적으로 문제가 생길 위험이 높은 데다 적게 움직이게 돼 치매에 걸릴 가능성이 높아지는 것으로 보인다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. <!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --></span></font></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><font size=\"2\" face=\"맑은 고딕\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><font size=\"2\" face=\"맑은 고딕\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121101_171/isuhani_1351741843505AHpnt_JPEG/8%B8%E9_%C7%D1%BE%E0.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"300\" height=\"198\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 300px; rheight: 198px\" id=\"20121101_171/isuhani_1351741843505AHpnt_JPEG/8%B8%E9_%C7%D1%BE%E0.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A5808641')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121101_171/isuhani_1351741843505AHpnt_JPEG/8%B8%E9_%C7%D1%BE%E0.jpg?type=w3\"></font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><font size=\"2\" face=\"맑은 고딕\"></font></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><font size=\"2\" face=\"맑은 고딕\"></font></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">석창포는 건망을 치료하며 머리를 좋게 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>원지와 함께 먹으면 눈과 귀가 밝아진다고 하였다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>연밥<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>연실<span lang=\"EN-US\">-</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">蓮實</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">은 신<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">神</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">-</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">정신<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>을 기르고 많이 먹으면 노여움을 멎게 하고 기쁘게 한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>오래 복용하면 즐거워진다고 하였다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>죽을 쑤어 먹는 것이 좋다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>자하거는 사람의 태반을 말하는데 건망증<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>가슴이 두근거리는 것<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>정신이 나간 것<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>정신이 없는 것<span lang=\"EN-US\">, </span>말이 많으나 일관성이 없는 것을 치료한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>마음을 편안하게 하고 혈<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">血</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">을 기르며 신<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></span></font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '바탕','serif'; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 바탕; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">神</span><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">)</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\">을 안정시키는 효능이 탁월하다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>쪄서 약에 넣거나 환으로 복용한다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>이것 한가지만 쪄서 먹어도 좋다고 하였다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span>자하거는 시중에서 구하기가 어려우니 한의원에서 자하거약침<span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span>태반약침<span lang=\"EN-US\">) </span>치료를 받는 방법도 있다<span lang=\"EN-US\">. </span></span></font></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></font></font>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric; WORD-BREAK: keep-all; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><font size=\"2\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-bidi-font-family: 굴림; mso-font-kerning: 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><!-- Removed Tag Filtered (o:p) --><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20121101_237/isuhani_135174187416287MbD_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8Logo-%C0%A5%BF%EB_%BB%E7%C0%CC%C1%EE_%C3%E0%BC%D2.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"193\" height=\"48\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 193px; rheight: 48px\" id=\"20121101_237/isuhani_135174187416287MbD_JPEG/%B0%E6%C8%F1%C0%CC%BC%F6%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF